const FETCH_ACCES_LEVELS_QUERY = `
query  {
  getLevels {
     date_created
     date_updated
     _id
     level_name
     description
     level_id
  }
}
`;

const FETCH_DESIGNATIONS =`
 query{
  getAllDesignations {
    designation_name
    level_id
    _id
    description
    date_created
    date_updated
    designation_id
    userlevels {
      level_name
      description
      date_created
      _id
      level_id

    }
  }
}
`

const FETCH_USERS =`
query ($paramId: String){
getUsers(paramId: $paramId) {
  designation_name
  description
  date_created
  date_updated
  level_id
  designation_id
  _id
  user {
    _id
    surname
    other_names
    patient_identifier
    designation_id    
    designation_id
    dob
    email
    phone_number
    gender
    status


  }
  level {
    date_created
    date_updated
    description
    level_name
    level_id

  }
}
}
`


const FETCH_PROGRAM = `
query {
  getPrograams {
    date_created
    date_updated
    programName
    description
    owner
    status
    id
  }
}

`
const FETCH_PROGRAM_ENROLL = `
query ($paramId: String){
  getUserPrograam {
   program_id
   createdAt
   id
   status
   userId
  }
}
`

const FETCH_VISITS = `
query {
  getVisits {
    id
    visitName
     visitNumber
     program_id
     date_created
     date_updated
     windowPeriod
     status
     description
  }
}
`

const FETCH_VISITS_SERVICES = `

query {
  getVisitServices {
    serviceName
    id
    visitId
    date_created
    date_updated
    status
    visitId
    description
    duration
  }
}
`
const FETCH_PROGRAMS = `
query GetPrograams {
  getPrograams {
    id
    programName
    status
  }
}
`

const FETCH_LAST_SERVICE_PROVIDED = `
query ($userId: String, $visitId: String, $id: ID) {
  getLastServiceProvided(userId: $userId, visitId: $visitId,id: $id) 
  {
    nextVisitdate
    serviceOfferedId
    status
    visitDate
    visitId
    visitType
    userId

  }
}
`

export {

  FETCH_ACCES_LEVELS_QUERY, 
  FETCH_DESIGNATIONS,
  FETCH_USERS,
  FETCH_PROGRAM,
  FETCH_PROGRAM_ENROLL,
  FETCH_VISITS,
  FETCH_VISITS_SERVICES,
  FETCH_PROGRAMS,
  FETCH_LAST_SERVICE_PROVIDED

}
